# Landis+Gyr UH50/T555 ESPHome Component

This is an ESPHome external component for reading data from Landis+Gyr UH50/T555 heat meters via UART.

## Usage
1. Add this repository as an external component in your ESPHome YAML.
2. Configure the UART and sensors as shown in `example.yaml`.

## Supported Sensors
- Energy consumption (kWh)
- Volume (m³)
- Inlet temperature (°C)
- Outlet temperature (°C)